# Le Poulet — Cursor Project Rules

## Project Overview

Le Poulet is a free, city-wide chicken hunt game. One person (the Chicken) hides somewhere
in the city — ideally a bar. Teams of hunters use GPS tracking, photo/video challenges, and
chaos power-up weapons to find them. First team to physically locate and photograph the
Chicken wins. Think manhunt meets bar crawl meets chaos engineering.

**Status:** MVP (Montreal-first, bilingual FR/EN)
**Domain:** lepoulet.gg
**Tagline:** Find the chicken. Win the city.

---

