## Visual Design

### Colors (Tailwind custom)
```
poulet-yellow:   #F5C518   (primary brand, CTAs)
poulet-red:      #E63946   (danger, Chicken role badge)
poulet-dark:     #1A1A2E   (backgrounds)
poulet-darker:   #16213E   (card backgrounds)
poulet-surface:  #0F3460   (elevated surfaces)
poulet-green:    #2DC653   (success, found states)
poulet-purple:   #8338EC   (chaos mode accent)
```

### Typography
- **Display:** Space Grotesk (bold, all caps for game codes)
- **Body:** Inter
- **Monospace:** JetBrains Mono (codes, coords)

### UI Principles
- Dark-first (game is played at night in bars)
- High contrast for outdoor/dim lighting readability
- Large tap targets (minimum 44px)
- Emoji-heavy — players have emoji avatars
- Animations: spring-based, never jarring
- Map is always the hero on game screens

